南都，换一种方式。
Nandu, a different way.
今天是元宵节，广东省支援湖北疫情防控医疗队前往武汉已半个月了。
Today is the Lantern Festival, Guangdong Province to support the Hubei epidemic prevention and control team to Wuhan has been half a month.
当万家团圆时，他们正义无反顾地奋战在抗疫最前线，南方医科大学珠江医院ICU主治医师王凯就是其中一员。
When the family reunion, they are fighting back in the forefront of the fight against the epidemic, the Southern Medical University Zhujiang Hospital ICU chief physician Wang Kai is one of them.
目前正在援助武汉的南方医科大学珠江医院ICU主治医师王凯。
Currently is assisting Wuhan Southern Medical University Zhujiang Hospital ICU chief physician Wang Kai.
以下是王凯写的一篇特殊的日记，写给相恋十年、同样是医生的女友。
The following is a special diary written by Wang Kai for a 10-year-old girlfriend who is also a doctor.
如果不是突然奔赴前线，春节期间王凯就要和家人商量与女友的婚事。
If it were not for his sudden departure to the front, Wang Kai would discuss his marriage with his girlfriend during the Spring Festival.
前几天两人恋爱十周年纪念日，平时就因工作原因时常爽约的王凯，在视频里对女友说，“我一定会回去，这是我们今天的约定，这一次，我不想再爽约了！” 病房里老太照顾老伴不离不弃今天是元宵节，团圆的日子，我们却相隔千里。
"I will definitely go back, this is our appointment today, this time, I don't want to meet again!" The old woman in the ward took care of his wife, today is Lantern Festival, reunion day, we are thousands of miles apart.
“全副武装”进病房，下班回酒店，这是我们每天的两点一线，今天也一样。
"Fully armed" into the ward, after work back to the hotel, this is our daily two-point line, the same today.
最近武汉白天的天气很暖和，但是对于穿防护服的我们来说，可不是件好事，因为真的很闷热，很快就会全身湿透，像淋雨一样。
The weather in Wuhan is very warm recently, but for us wearing protective clothing, is not a good thing, because it is really stuffy, will soon be wet, like the rain.
病房里一些危重病人的病情还是很让人担忧。
The condition of some critically ill patients in the ward is still very worrying.
我管的一个老年病人今天病情还是不太好，血氧下降得很厉害，一直照顾他的老伴在我们强烈建议下，去门诊查了个CT，也怀疑是新冠病毒感染。
One of my elderly patients is still not very well today, his blood oxygen is falling so much that he's been taking care of his wife who, under our strong recommendation, went to the clinic for a CT scan, also suspected of a new crown virus infection.
老太太对自己的安危并没有很担心，反而全身心扑在她的老伴儿身上。
The old lady was not very worried about her own safety, but devoted herself to her old companion.
子女都不在身边，两个老人从疫情爆发后始终相互扶持，我相信他们这一生都在相互扶持，直到现在也依然不离不弃。
The children are not around, the two old people from the outbreak of mutual support from the outbreak, I believe they have been supporting each other throughout their lives, and still do not abandon.
我和南方医院的吴凤医生给老太太送了一些抗病毒药物和防护口罩，还留了手机号给她，提醒她注意自己的身体，有需要及时联系我们。
Dr. Wu Feng of the Southern Hospital and I sent the old lady some antiviral drugs and face masks, and left her a cell phone number to remind her of her body and need to contact us in time.
支援武汉女友含泪帮改机票下班离开医院，走在武汉寂寥的大街上，我不由得想起了你，在广州的你是否也已下班了，是否也在等着我回去报一声平安。
Wuhan girlfriend tearful help to change tickets left the hospital, walking in Wuhan lonely street, I can not help but think of you, whether you have also been off duty in Guangzhou, whether I am also waiting for me to report back safe.
我们高中相识，相恋十年，高中毕业后都选择了学医，但分隔两个城市。
We met in high school, fell in love for 10 years, high school graduates choose to study medicine, but separated the two cities.
现在回想起来，几年的异地恋我们能坚持下来，真的很不容易。
In retrospect, several years of long-distance love we can insist on, really not easy.
同为医务人员的你，当然深知此次疫情的险峻。
As a medical worker, of course, you are well aware of the severity of the epidemic.
所以，当我决定奔赴武汉、而且是在大年三十突然离别时，电话那头的你担心得快哭了。
So when I decided to go to Wuhan, and it was in the Chinese New Year's Eve when suddenly parted, the other end of the phone you worried almost cry.
但你了解我，知道我的性情，也明白我的固执，你知道我只要有机会，一定会去武汉支援的。
But you know me, know my temperament, also understand my stubbornness, you know that as long as I have the opportunity, I will go to Wuhan to support.
担心归担心，但你也明白，我这么做是对的。
Worried about, but you know, I did the right thing.
你是一名老党员了，所以也很理解并支持我的选择，还立刻帮我改签机票。
You are an old Party member, so also understand and support my choice, and help me to change the ticket immediately.
我从阜阳老家返回广州，随即立刻奔赴前线。
I returned to Guangzhou from my hometown of Fuyang and immediately went to the front.
说来惭愧，作为一名ICU医生，平时生活本来就不规律，跟你约定好的事情，常常因为科里有病人需要抢救而取消，所以你总是开玩笑地叫我“鸽子王”。
Ashamed, as an ICU doctor, ordinary life is not regular, and you agreed with the things, often because there are patients need to rescue the cancellation, so you always jokingly called me "pigeon King."
今年过年好不容易才能休几天假，本来计划去你父母家拜访，并商量一下我们的婚事，谁曾想疫情爆发，我回家第二天就返回广州了，都没来得及去给她父母拜个年，我又一次脸皮厚地放了你“鸽子”。
I had planned to visit your parents and discuss our marriage, who had thought of the outbreak, and returned to Guangzhou the next day before I could pay her parents a New Year's holiday.
奔赴前线自觉亏欠女友又庆幸来武汉后，每次跟你视频，我都跟你保证，我一定注意安全，一定会平安回去的。
Go to the front and feel grateful to my girlfriend after coming to Wuhan, every time I video with you, I assure you, I must pay attention to safety, will go back safely.
但你我心里都清楚，身在前线抢救病人，哪能百分之百保证自己的安全。
But you and I know in our hearts, in front of the rescue patients, can not guarantee 100% of their own safety.
有些人经常会问，你们谈了那么久为什么还不结婚。
Some people often ask why you haven't been married for so long.
学医的都清楚，一个医学生要成为一名合格的医生需要多少年的努力与付出，所以我真的很惭愧让你等了那么久。
Medical students know how many years it takes for a medical student to become a qualified doctor, so I'm really ashamed to have kept you waiting so long.
大学时我们是异地恋，我没能照顾好你，本以为我们终于可以结婚了，我可以好好补偿你了，结果我又突然奔赴前线。
We were apart in college, I couldn't take care of you, I thought we could finally get married, I could make it up to you, and then I suddenly went to the front.
然而现在，在觉得亏欠你的同时，我又有一点庆幸，庆幸我们到现在还没结婚。
Now, however, while I feel indebted to you, I am a little grateful that we are not married yet.
因为万一，我是说万一，万一我有什么意外，你的人生还可以有其他选择。
Because in case, I mean just in case, in case anything should happen to me, you have other options in your life.
就在前几天，2020年1月31日，是我们恋爱十周年纪念日。
Just a few days ago, on 31 January 2020, we celebrated our tenth anniversary of love.
隔着视频，你说：“是的啊，你还记得今天啊，这个日子你看你都没什么表示。
Through the video, you said, "Yes, you remember today, and you didn't even look at me this day.
”其实你知道我今天还在值班，很晚才回来。
"Actually, you know I was on duty today, and I came back very late.
你说：“所以你一定要回来，慢慢补给我。
You said, "So you must come back and slowly replenish me.
”我顿时一阵心痛：你才不会在意什么纪念日和礼物，你在意的只有我能安全回去。
"I felt a pain in my heart: you don't care about anniversaries or gifts; all you care about is if I get back safely.
我说：“好啊，我一定会回去，带你买你想要的礼物。
I said, "OK, I will go back and bring you the present you want.
这是我们今天的约定，这一次，我不想再爽约了。
This is our appointment for today. This time, I don't want to meet again.
”想到此处，我不由得加快了脚步，想尽快赶回酒店，那里还有一个人在担心我——只想牵着你的手，跟你一起走下去。
I hastened to get back to the inn as fast as I could, and there was a man there who was worried about me - just wanted to take your hand and go with you.
